%%% @doc This is gen_server module that responsible for handling MSCs operations.
%%%
%%% @copyright 2012 ITI Egypt.
%%% @author Esraa Adel <esraa.elmelegy@hotmail.com>
%%% @author Sherif Ashraf <sherif_ashraf89@hotmail.com>
